  },
  "comment": "onAir Panel 1 IP is a rugged IP65, full-spectrum LED soft light with a 1×1 format that is capable of facing all of the elements, outdoors or in. Ready to go on-location for any broadcast setting, onAir Panel 1 IP features a superior quality of white light with high CRI/ TLC and TM-30 scores; a smooth 16-bit dimming curve and +/- green adjustment, an emulated redshift, and the ability to produce a pop of color to achieve the exact look you are aiming to create along with built-in, customizable effects accessible from the onboard control menu. Easily switch mounting options from Jr Pin to Omega Bracket on a rugged build, designed with a drop-in slot to ensure ease of use when changing accessories. PWM, DMX, RDM, CRMX, Art-Net, sACN, and an onboard control option ensure camera-ready use. An optional 28 VDC input via 3-pin XLR powers the fixture from an external battery pack to add increased flexibility for all of your remote needs.",
